<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="./styles.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.4.1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Load Quiz</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<%- include('../views/partials/header'); %>

<div class="file-upload mt-4">
    <h2>Upload Quiz Text File</h2>
    <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="mt-3">
        <input type="file" name="quizFile" required>
        <button type="submit">Upload & Load Quiz</button>
    </form>
</div>

    <div class="container">
        <hr />

        <h2>Instructions for Uploading a Quiz</h2>
        <p>Creating and uploading a quiz is simple. Just follow these steps:</p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled font-weight-bold">
            <li>1. Create a new Text File.</li>
            <li>2. Follow the guide in README.md (can be found on our GitHub) for creating quizzes via text file.</li>
            <li>3. Add questions and customize options.</li>
            <li>4. Save your quiz with a <code>.txt</code> extension.</li>
        </ul>
        <hr />
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Actions Section -->
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col text-center">
                <h2 class="font-weight-bold mb-4">More Actions</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center mb-2 mt-2">
                <form action="/myquizzes" method="POST">
                    <button class="btn btn-dark btn-lg btn-block w-75" type="submit">My Quizzes</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center mb-2 mt-2">
                <form action="/create" method="POST">
                    <button class="btn btn-dark btn-lg btn-block w-75" type="submit">Create Quiz</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

<!-- <%- include('../views/partials/footer'); %> -->

</body>
</html>